caption: If you’re interested in ordering from here, this is your sign to not waste your time or money. First, my food was suppose to deliver at 12:00 after placing it at 10:00. It came at 1:10am.. I called the restaurant, they said (at 12:00) it should be there in 15 minutes, I asked if they were delivering the food or if ChowNow will. They said ChowNow is responsible for all deliveries. (After speaking to 3 workers because they clearly acted as if they didn’t know they partake in 3rd party apps) After connecting with ChowNow at 12:30, they said the restaurant suggested it would be another 20 minutes and the restaurant delivers the food. For a salad. Empanada. And burger. This is very disappointing. I finally receive my food. Cold. Wrong burger. Toppings I paid extra for are not present. My “salad” was kale and avocado. No quinoa, no vegetables, no dressing... This restaurant should be ashamed of themselves! I will be requesting a full refund but I ask you all to not bother with this restaurant if you’re reading this review. Owner, please do not bother commenting back and save the pity apology.
